OL,5, A group of teachers exchanged WhatsApp 
OL,6, messages with "degrading" references to
OL,7, disabled primary school pupils, BBC    
OL,8, Scotland can reveal.                   
OL,10,FThe staff at schools in Aberdeenshire  
OL,11,Ffaced an internal investigation, but   
OL,12,Fthe affected pupils' parents were not  
OL,13,Finformed.                              
OL,15,FScotland's children commissioner said  
OL,16,Fthe parents should be told.            
OL,18,FAberdeenshire Council has said the     
OL,19,Fmessages were "inappropriate and       
OL,20,Funprofessional".                       
